        <para>08REA and 08RGA provide radio power and ground directly from the battery to minimize electrical noise on
            the line.
        </para>
        <para>The cable is coiled up under the instrument panel as shown above in 08REA, and is of sufficient length to
            route to the back of the Travelcrew cab.
        </para>
        <para>The wiring is located in the center of the header console in the cab for 08RGA.</para>
        <figure id="f7300094" figsize="pg-wide">
